      • stopAllAimlessDriveTasks

        public void stopAllAimlessDriveTasks()
        If diversion is enabled, this method must be called after scheduling in order to make sure that no vehicle is moving aimlessly.

        The reason: the destination/goal had been removed before scheduling (e.g. by calling the removeAwaitingRequestsFromAllSchedules() method)
